  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "M\u1ED9t ng\xE0y n\u1ECD \xCA-li-s\xEA \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn Su-nam, n\u01A1i \u0111\xF3 c\xF3 m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE0n b\xE0 c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa v\u1ECB. Ch\u1ECB n\u0103n n\u1EC9 \xCA-li-s\xEA \u1EDF l\u1EA1i v\xE0 d\xF9ng b\u1EEFa. Cho n\xEAn m\u1ED7i khi \xCA-li-s\xEA \u0111i ngang qua v\xF9ng \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EC1u gh\xE9 d\xF9ng b\u1EEFa. "), mdx("h6", {
