  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng ta h\xE3y l\xE0m m\u1ED9t ph\xF2ng tr\xEAn m\xE1i nh\xE0 v\xE0 \u0111\u1EB7t m\u1ED9t c\xE1i gi\u01B0\u1EDDng cho \xF4ng ta. Ch\xFAng ta c\u0169ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EB7t m\u1ED9t c\xE1i b\xE0n, m\u1ED9t c\xE1i gh\u1EBF, m\u1ED9t c\xE1i \u0111\xE8n trong \u0111\xF3. R\u1ED3i m\u1ED7i khi \xF4ng \u1EA5y gh\xE9 qua th\xEC s\u1EBD \u1EDF \u0111\xF3.\" "), mdx("h6", {
