  }, "v44"), mdx("p", null, "Sau khi \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB ph\xE1t b\xE1nh cho h\u1ECD, m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0103n no n\xEA v\xE0 c\xF2n d\u01B0 l\u1EA1i y nh\u01B0 l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA \u0111\xE3 ph\xE1n."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
